<div class="container mt-5"> <div class="col-md-7 mb-4 textoComponentes"> <h2 class="mb-4">We Facilitate Your Investment</h2> <p> The key to any investment is the trust between parties, which is why you will always have the property document in your name and control over your money. To ensure this, a document is signed through digital means with full security and legal endorsement to provide you with complete peace of mind and transparency. </p> <div class="facilitamos-items"> <img src="./Iconos/iconosrealissa/r4.webp" alt="magnifying glass"> <div> <h4>FORMATION OF AN LLC (LIMITED LIABILITY COMPANY)</h4> <p> We assist you in setting up an LLC, which is the legal instrument necessary to safeguard the purchase of the lot and the development of the construction project. </p> </div> </div> <div class="facilitamos-items"> <img src="./Iconos/iconosrealissa/r5.webp" alt="business"> <div> <h4> OPERATING AGREEMENT (SOCIAL CONTRACT) </h4> <p> This is the document that defines the purpose of the LLC, in this case: purchasing a lot, building a house, selling it upon completion, distributing the profits, and dissolving the LLC. This document outlines the operation of the LLC and the participation of each member based on their contribution, among other aspects of the investment made. </p> </div> </div> </div></div>